snippet.title: Johnny Depp's lawyers return to the High Court
snippet.description:
Actor Johnny Depp is trying to overturn a High Court libel case ruling that he assaulted his ex-wife Amber Heard.

His legal team claim to have fresh evidence, including proof that Ms Heard lied about donating her $7million divorce settlement to charity.
